title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Royal Aircraft Factory SE 5 - version 0.0.1
description:
In this video we will look at the Royal Aircraft Factory SE 5 which has been released today. The aircraft is still in development phase but you can already fly pretty nice with this aircraft.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
